  "body": "### Describe the feature\n\nHi mates, currently the `vars` scope is super convenient but usually the kind of data(keys) used is stored already in some sort of vault or password manager which is actually more secure. Could be possible instead of store directly the values, store a command that allow to safely retrieve those values ? Something like `hardhat vars set VAR_KEY --command COMMAND_TO_GET_VALUE`.  Thanks in advanced\n\n### Search terms\n\n_No response_",
